    "Although some solutions have been proposed, such as displaying AI explanations [8] and forcing people to think more effortfully In traditional AI-assisted decision-making, when humans disagree with AI's suggestions (and only find parts of AI's reasons applaudable), it is difficult for humans to decide whether and how much to adopt AI's suggestion.",
    "(B) In our proposed Human-AI Deliberation, we provide opportunities for the human and the AI model to deliberate on conflicting opinions by discussing related evidence and arguments.",
